系d大神好多fans。然後好曲折離奇⋯曖昧過一段時間佢都冇出黎，佢個形象一直都係好好冷 悶騷型。直到兩個月前我地見面，其實原本報著一個約炮名義去見，因為我地都有玩sex phone 但係出到黎又冇搞嘢叼⋯ 都唔知佢想點<br />\n好啦咁然後一個月前有一晚又出黎了，都係三更半夜。補充一下 佢兩次都飲左酒 其實冇醉都係扮，叼真系醉左就返屋企拉係咪先。然後第二次有攬下 都冇做咩過界行為。陪到我早上啦，好啦咁返去我wts問佢，一起啦好冇？佢話大家考慮清楚 然後訓醒我地第日有出黎唱K，不過返到去wts佢都係冷。但據我所知 佢對我已經好好<br />\n<br />\n好撚怪噶佢就係 wts好冷 試過一個月唔復人嗰種，對住我試過消失一兩日。但係真人好nice<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打絲打幫手諗下究竟問題出現係邊？系佢問題定我問題？如果佢真系冇feel就唔會出黎第二次。補充一下，佢樣一般 可以帶出街嘅類型。我，樣好 衰在矮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真系好撚煩啊啊啊啊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n系乜撚呀又"},{"pid":"02bf22a63e904997cca8bb41ec6d7eddf98dc6dd","tid":263292,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T19:52:38.000Z","msg":"平平個po又上熱門啦"},{"pid":"46c65acb64e9c0338634f3da4d7c61e4b6e2f776","tid":263292,"uid":85041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T19:53:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你喜啦</blockquote><br />\n嗨</blockquote><br />\n嗨</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 握手做朋友</blockquote><br />\n握握手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a15fca0177358c41d9d7bd2eabdc815cffd5459","tid":263292,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T20:03:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你喜啦</blockquote><br />\n嗨</blockquote><br />\n嗨</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 握手做朋友</blockquote><br />\n握握手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做個好朋友"},{"pid":"45616d26150a81ef118687a890ba0597624fc96d","tid":263292,"uid":85041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T20:04:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你喜啦</blo